@ItaOKelly @campaignforleo suffers with vagina envy. Establishment default position.

However, we are scraping the bottom of a rotten barrel to find leaders. 

The in breeding of FF/FG/Labour is an ever decreasing gene pool, so no woman, from that pool, would be an improvement anyway.

@ItaOKelly "We are fast becoming a laughing stock on the world political stage."

We ARE a laughing stock. 

That has nothing to do with no women in positions of authority and power, it has everything to do with the Irish government behaving like clowns whenever they go anywhere.
